docs.name: Zillow Metrics (Counties): Median Sale Price per Sq. Ft. - Garfield, OK
docs.description: Median of sale prices when divided by the square footage of a home. This data is calculated by Zillow Real Estate Research (www.zillow.com/research) using their database of 110 million homes.

docs.name: Zillow Metrics (Cities): Sold for Loss (%) - Gunnison, CO
docs.description: The percentage of homes that sold for less than the previous purchase price (e.g. a home purchased for $250k and then sold for $225k). This excludes foreclosure transactions.
